{
  "stem": "8895.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother must have had enough money to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had the platinum, and this-- my father maybe earned [INAUDIBLE] in there or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was quite clever doing that, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had fantastic clientele.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The top [INAUDIBLE] 10,000 [INAUDIBLE] thousands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's an-- for instance, a lady would say she is coming, and she-- she wasn't to be interrupted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she had a chauffeur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had-- she had-- servants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had to wear gloves when serving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Embroidered-- everything embroidered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And hats, things, head gear, and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People like that, she had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mining, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had mines, coal mines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you can image.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I remember, but maybe he did something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't get a job or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very clever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we had such-- such difficulties with-- with staying in Poland, he once, went to the-- went to the police and went to the highest man in the police.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What would he be like?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like-- like a commissioner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he waited till he came out and followed him home, and he knew where he lived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Next day he went and knocked at the door, and his wife was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a gentleman, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, nobody could close the door on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he introduced himself and told us a story that [INAUDIBLE] was so difficult.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Could she help us?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we became friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And through her husband, the life of my mother and my life was bad, later on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She fled with us to-- to-- to Russia, to Katowice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Together we fled with this woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were taken by the police, my mother and I, because my mother had stacks of new money, completely new.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
